text.tspan: Aqua Air we at a crucial stage in their business when they approached us. They
had been established for 15 years and had a pretty impressive client list. The
business was ready to be taken to the next level but had a very old website,
no real branding and a great range of products that needed to be represented
to their full potential. Push My Profile undertook a complete companywide
rebrand over 12 months including a range of new websites, sales and marketing
literature, a complete rebrand and rename of the existing product range as well
additions of new products that helped capture new markets. A great project and
a great result. The company image is now as sharp and hi-tech as the products
Aqua Air sell and the service they carry out.
You can spend years creating a great company, with great products and a great
service. We can make sure it is fresh and modern and that it helps you generate
business helping you prosper and expand.
